{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"AudioNodeOptions","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/AudioNode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/channelCount\"><code>channelCount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/channelCountMode\"><code>channelCountMode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/channelInterpretation\"><code>channelInterpretation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/context\"><code>context</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/numberOfInputs\"><code>numberOfInputs</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/numberOfOutputs\"><code>numberOfOutputs</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/connect\"><code>connect()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/disconnect\"><code>disconnect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API\">Web Audio API</a>&nbsp;的&nbsp;<strong><code>AudioNodeOptions</code></strong>&nbsp;字典指定了创建新&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a>&nbsp;对象时可使用的选项.</span></p>\n\n<p><code>AudioNodeOptions</code>&nbsp;继承自不同类型的音频节点构造函数的选项对象.&nbsp;例如&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnalyserNode/AnalyserNode\"><code>AnalyserNode.AnalyserNode</code></a>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GainNode/GainNode\"><code>GainNode.GainNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var audioNodeOptions = {\n  \"channelCount\" : 2,\n  \"channelCountMode\" : \"max\",\n  \"channelInterpretation\" : \"discrete\"\n}</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"channelcount\"><em>channelCount</em> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n <dd>Represents an integer used to determine how many channels are used when <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API/Basic_concepts_behind_Web_Audio_API#up-mixing_and_down-mixing\">up-mixing and down-mixing</a> connections to any inputs to the node. (See <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/channelCount\"><code>AudioNode.channelCount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> for more information.) Its usage and precise definition depend on the value of <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>AudioNodeOptions.channelCountMode</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"channelcount_2\"><em>channelCount</em>Mode <span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n <dd>Represents an enumerated value describing the way channels must be matched between the node's inputs and outputs. (See <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/channelCountMode\"><code>AudioNode.channelCountMode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> for more information including default values.)</dd>\n <dt id=\"channelinterpretation\"><em>channelInterpretation</em> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n <dd>Represents an enumerated value describing the meaning of the channels. This interpretation will define how audio <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API/Basic_concepts_behind_Web_Audio_API#up-mixing_and_down-mixing\">up-mixing and down-mixing</a> will happen.<br>\n The possible values are <code>\"speakers\"</code> or <code>\"discrete\"</code>. (See <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioNode/channelCountMode\"><code>AudioNode.channelCountMode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> for more information including default values.)</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/webaudio/#audionodeoptions\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Audio API<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">AudioNodeOptions</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"浏览器兼容性","title":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>55.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/53\" title=\"Released on 2017-04-18.\">53</a> (53)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>42</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td>55.0</td>\n   <td>53.0 (53)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>42</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>55.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"Web Audio API 的 AudioNodeOptions 字典指定了创建新 AudioNode 对象时可使用的选项.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/audionode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/audionode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/AudioNode","title":"AudioNodeOptions"}],"pageTitle":"AudioNodeOptions | MDN","noIndexing":true}}